  "title": "Service Advisor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Benefits:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Opportunities for career growth and professional development.</p>\n<p>• Performance-based bonuses</p>\n<p>• Yearly appraisal for promotion and increment</p>\n<p>• Positive company culture – open and transparent communication, diversity and inclusion</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<p>• Perform test ride (bike)</p>\n<p>• Provide knowledgeable advice and recommendations on motorcycle maintenance and repair services based on manufacturer guidelines and customer needs.</p>\n<p>• Schedule service appointments and coordinate with mechanic to ensure efficient workflow and timely completion of service jobs</p>\n<p>• Communicate with customers regarding service timelines, updates, and any additional repairs or maintenance needed</p>\n<p>• Generate quotations, invoices and process payments accurately</p>\n<p>• Follow up with customers after service completion to ensure satisfaction and address any additional needs.</p>\n<p>• Any other duties as assigned by Manager</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>• Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</p>\n<p>• Customer-focused attitude with a commitment to delivering exceptional service</p>\n<p>• Minimum class 2A license with 1 year riding experience</p>",
